BEGIN:VTODO
UID:TODO-65A34DA1-B2AD-4A12-AC8C-99C9742192CC
DTSTAMP:20260416T173838Z
SUMMARY:Post listing on PROPEL
DESCRIPTION:• see emails from Deb Phillis on [2026-01-23 Fri] and [2026-01-
 29\n  Thu].\n• lead time is several months\, try Round 5 (approx. April) a
 nd Round 1\n  (approx. August) for Fall 2027.
